":176,"date":177,"citedRange":178,"ptr":179,"ref":181,"inscriptionDate":177,"title":183,"citation":184,"uri":185,"year":177},"Manni Piraino","1980","1804-1805, no.42, pl. 11",{"target":180},"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/IFH7SBMP",{"_":182,"target":182},"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001765","Nuove iscrizioni dall'acropoli di Gela","\u003Cspan>M.T. Manni Piraino, «Nuove iscrizioni dall’acropoli di Gela», in \u003Ci>Philias Charin. Miscellanea di studi classici in onore di Eugenio Manni\u003C/i>, vol. 5, 6 voll. (Rome, 1980), 1767–1831\u003C/span>","https://www.zotero.org/groups/isicily/items/IFH7SBMP",{"editor":187,"principal":190,"contributors":193,"change":204},{"_":188,"ref":189},"Jonathan Prag","#JP",{"_":191,"ref":192},"Valentina Mignosa","#VM",[194,197,200],{"_":188,"xml:id":195,"ref":196},"JP","https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537",{"_":191,"xml:id":198,"ref":199},"VM","https://orcid.org/0000-0002-7122-2511",{"_":201,"xml:id":202,"ref":203},"Simona Stoyanova","SS","https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3914-9569",{"_":205,"when":206,"who":192},"Valentina Mignosa added metadata, text","2021-10-14",{"n":95,"url":96,"height":97,"width":98,"desc":99,"surfaceType":100},[],[210],"Agostiniani, Forthcoming, IAS2",[212],"UE7VX29V",[214,214,215,18,23,27,216,217,218,219,220,221,222,123],"isic020759",{"_":4},"herbessus (?)","montagna di marzo","sicilia","sicily","agrigento","museo regionale archeologico pietro griffo","sikel",[],{"title":225,"body":226,"divs":227,"editions":254,"images":275,"handnote":281},"ISic020759. ISic020759","\u003Cdiv id=\"editions\">\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"scx-Grek\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"scx-Grek\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"πυρρια\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"πυρρια\">πυρρια\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Unknown\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive-transliteration\" lang=\"scx-Latn\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"scx-Latn\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>pyrria \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"scx-Grek\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"scx-Grek\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"πυρρια\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"πυρρια\">ΠΥΡΡΙΑ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Unknown\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic-transliteration\" lang=\"scx-Latn\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"scx-Latn\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>PYRRIA\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic020759_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic020759_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic020759.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic020759-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text after Agostiniani, in Agostiniani, Albanese Procelli 2018.\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The masculine name Πυρρίας is common in Greek, also in Sicily. Πυρρι[ας] occurs for example in the environment of Gela, as shown by the graffito on black-glazed Attic skyphos (\u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic020500\" target=\"_blank\">ISic020500\u003C/a>; \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/65P7AM6N\" target=\"_blank\">Arena IGASM II[2]\u003C/a>, no. 54, pl. 19.3; \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/IFH7SBMP\" target=\"_blank\">Manni Piraino 1980\u003C/a>, p. 1804-1805, no. 42, pl. 11; \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ\" target=\"_blank\">SEG 29.0874\u003C/a>) and by a defixio (\u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/65P7AM6N\" target=\"_blank\">Arena IGASM 2[2]\u003C/a>, no. 45, l. 9), and it would therefore be no surprise to find it in the context of Montagna di Marzo. But we can also assume a masculine nominative case ending in -α, alien to Greek, but conceivable for other cases from Montagna di Marzo (Agostiniani 2018, p. 193), such as Ταμυρα (MMA 83; \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic020752\" target=\"_blank\">ISic020752\u003C/a>) or Κακρυολα (MMA 81; \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic020761\" target=\"_blank\">ISic020761\u003C/a>). Or, since the inscription is on a pyxis, a vessel generally associated with predominantly female use (Agostiniani 2018, 193, n.147), the name could be a feminine one, not otherwise attested in Greek.\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>From a palaeographical point of view, it is interesting to note the use of 'normal' alpha (and not the arrow-shaped type), the rho type without the lower stroke (as occurs elsewhere and in the East tomb 31) and the upsilon type with a vertical bar, when most inscriptions use the V-type.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Agostiniani Forthcoming MMA 44a \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002519\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002519\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 29.0874 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manni Piraino 1980 1804-1805, no.42, pl. 11 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001765\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001765\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Arena 2002 54, pl. XIX.3 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001373\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001373\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Agostiniani, Albanese Procelli 2018 193, fig. 119 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001345\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001345\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">  Line 1    \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[228,231,234,237,240,242,245,248,251],{"id":229,"html":230},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"scx-Grek\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"scx-Grek\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"πυρρια\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"πυρρια\">πυρρια\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Unknown\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive-transliteration\" lang=\"scx-Latn\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"scx-Latn\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>pyrria \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"scx-Grek\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"scx-Grek\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"πυρρια\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"πυρρια\">ΠΥΡΡΙΑ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Unknown\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic-transliteration\" lang=\"scx-Latn\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"scx-Latn\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>PYRRIA\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>",{"id":232,"html":233},"facsimile-images","\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic020759_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic020759_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic020759.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic020759-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>",{"id":235,"html":236},"apparatus","\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text after Agostiniani, in Agostiniani, Albanese Procelli 2018.\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"id":238,"html":239},"translation","\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>",{"id":238,"html":241},"\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>",{"id":243,"html":244},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The masculine name Πυρρίας is common in Greek, also in Sicily. Πυρρι[ας] occurs for example in the environment of Gela, as shown by the graffito on black-glazed Attic skyphos (\u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic020500\" target=\"_blank\">ISic020500\u003C/a>; \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/65P7AM6N\" target=\"_blank\">Arena IGASM II[2]\u003C/a>, no. 54, pl. 19.3; \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/IFH7SBMP\" target=\"_blank\">Manni Piraino 1980\u003C/a>, p. 1804-1805, no. 42, pl. 11; \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ\" target=\"_blank\">SEG 29.0874\u003C/a>) and by a defixio (\u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/65P7AM6N\" target=\"_blank\">Arena IGASM 2[2]\u003C/a>, no. 45, l. 9), and it would therefore be no surprise to find it in the context of Montagna di Marzo. But we can also assume a masculine nominative case ending in -α, alien to Greek, but conceivable for other cases from Montagna di Marzo (Agostiniani 2018, p. 193), such as Ταμυρα (MMA 83; \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic020752\" target=\"_blank\">ISic020752\u003C/a>) or Κακρυολα (MMA 81; \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic020761\" target=\"_blank\">ISic020761\u003C/a>). Or, since the inscription is on a pyxis, a vessel generally associated with predominantly female use (Agostiniani 2018, 193, n.147), the name could be a feminine one, not otherwise attested in Greek.\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>From a palaeographical point of view, it is interesting to note the use of 'normal' alpha (and not the arrow-shaped type), the rho type without the lower stroke (as occurs elsewhere and in the East tomb 31) and the upsilon type with a vertical bar, when most inscriptions use the V-type.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":246,"html":247},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Agostiniani Forthcoming MMA 44a \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002519\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002519\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 29.0874 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manni Piraino 1980 1804-1805, no.42, pl. 11 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001765\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001765\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Arena 2002 54, pl. XIX.3 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001373\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001373\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Agostiniani, Albanese Procelli 2018 193, fig. 119 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001345\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001345\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":249,"html":250},"handnote","  Line 1    ",{"id":252,"html":253},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[255,257,261,263,267,268,271,272],{"html":256},"Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa",{"id":258,"lang":259,"html":260},"edition-interpretive","scx-Grek","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"scx-Grek\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"πυρρια\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"πυρρια\">πυρρια\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",{"html":262},"Unknown",{"id":264,"lang":265,"html":266},"edition-interpretive-transliteration","scx-Latn","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"scx-Latn\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>pyrria \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",{"html":256},{"id":269,"lang":259,"html":270},"edition-diplomatic","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"scx-Grek\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"πυρρια\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"πυρρια\">ΠΥΡΡΙΑ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",{"html":262},{"id":273,"lang":265,"html":274},"edition-diplomatic-transliteration","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"scx-Latn\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>PYRRIA\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",[276,278],{"image":96,"thumb":277,"title":99},"ISic020759_tiled-thumb.tif",{"image":279,"thumb":280,"title":99},"ISic020759.jpg","ISic020759-thumb.jpg",[],"\u003C?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>\n\u003C?xml-model href=\"https://epidoc.stoa.org/schema/latest/tei-epidoc.rng\" type=\"application/xml\" schematypens=\"http://relaxng.org/ns/structure/1.0\"?>\n\u003C?xml-model href=\"../schematron/ircyr-checking.sch\" schematypens=\"http://purl.oclc.org/dsdl/schematron\"?>\n\u003CTEI xmlns=\"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0\" xmlns:xi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude\" xml:lang=\"en\">\n    \u003CteiHeader>\n        \u003CfileDesc>\n            \u003CtitleStmt>\n                \u003Ctitle>ISic020759\u003C/title>\n                \u003Ceditor ref=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/editor>\n                \u003Cprincipal ref=\"#VM\">Valentina Mignosa\u003C/principal>\n                \u003Cfunder>John Fell OUP Research Fund\u003C/funder>\n                \u003Cfunder>\u003Cref target=\"https://cordis.europa.eu/project/id/885040\">ERC Advanced Grant no.885040\u003C/ref>\u003C/funder>\n                \u003CrespStmt>\n                    \u003Cname xml:id=\"JP\" ref=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Cresp>project direction, template development and general editor\u003C/resp>\n                \u003C/respStmt>\n                \u003CrespStmt>\n                    \u003Cname xml:id=\"VM\" ref=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0002-7122-2511\">Valentina Mignosa\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Cresp>original data collection and editing, encoding text in Epidoc\u003C/resp>\n                \u003C/respStmt>\n                \u003CrespStmt>\n                    \u003Cname xml:id=\"SS\" ref=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3914-9569\">Simona Stoyanova\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Cresp>standardisation of template and tidying up encoding\u003C/resp>\n                \u003C/respStmt>\n            \u003C/titleStmt>\n            \u003CpublicationStmt>\n                \u003Cauthority>I.Sicily\u003C/authority>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"filename\">ISic020759\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"TM\"/>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"EDR\"/>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"EDH\"/>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"EDCS\"/>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"PHI\"/>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"URI\">http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic020759\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cavailability>\n                    \u003Clicence target=\"http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/\">Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.\u003C/licence>\n                \u003C/availability>\n            \u003C/publicationStmt>\n            \u003CsourceDesc>\n                \u003CmsDesc>\n                    \u003CmsIdentifier>\n                        \u003Ccountry>Italy\u003C/country>\n                        \u003Cregion>Sicily\u003C/region>\n                        \u003Csettlement>Agrigento\u003C/settlement> \u003C!-- and/or Deposito della Soprintendenza di Enna a Piazza Armerina (Palazzo Trigona) -->\n                        \u003Crepository role=\"museum\" ref=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/museum/130\">Museo Regionale Archeologico Pietro Griffo\u003C/repository> \u003C!-- and/or http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/museum/6, Biblioteca Comunale / Museo Archeologico ??? -->\n                        \u003Cidno type=\"inventory\"/>\n                        \u003CaltIdentifier>\n                            \u003Csettlement>Montagna di Marzo\u003C/settlement>\n                            \u003Crepository/>\n                            \u003Cidno type=\"old\"/>\n                        \u003C/altIdentifier>\n                    \u003C/msIdentifier>\n                    \u003CmsContents>\n                        \u003CtextLang mainLang=\"scx\">Sikel\u003C/textLang>    \n                    \u003C/msContents>\n                    \u003CphysDesc>\n                        \u003CobjectDesc>\n                            \u003CsupportDesc>\n                                \u003Csupport>\n                                    \u003Cp>Pyxis lid.\u003C/p>\n                                    \u003Cmaterial ana=\"#material.clay.fired\" ref=\"https://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/131.html\">ceramic\u003C/material>\n                                    \u003CobjectType ana=\"#object.vessel.pyxis\" ref=\"http://kerameikos.org/id/pyxis\">pyxis, lid\u003C/objectType>\n                                    \u003Cdimensions>\n                                        \u003Cheight unit=\"cm\"/>\n                                        \u003Cdim type=\"diameter\" subtype=\"base\" unit=\"cm\"/>\n                                        \u003Cdim type=\"diameter\" subtype=\"foot\" unit=\"cm\"/>\n                                        \u003Cwidth unit=\"cm\"/>\n                                        \u003Cdepth unit=\"cm\"/>\n                                    \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003C/support>\n                                \u003Ccondition ana=\"#condition.complete\"/>\n                            \u003C/supportDesc>\n                            \u003ClayoutDesc>\n                                \u003Clayout>\n                                    \u003Crs ana=\"#execution.scratched\" ref=\"https://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/9\">scratched\u003C/rs>\n                                    \u003Cp/> \u003C!-- add this information -->\n                                    \u003Cdamage ana=\"#text_condition.complete\"/>\n                                \u003C/layout>\n                            \u003C/layoutDesc>\n                        \u003C/objectDesc>\n                        \u003ChandDesc>\n                            \u003ChandNote>\n                                \u003C!-- Based on Glyph table: alpha22; iota01; pi13; rho01; rho12; upsilon06. -->\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line1\" to=\"line1\">Line 1\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"letterHeight\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\"/>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                            \u003C/handNote>\n                        \u003C/handDesc>\n                    \u003C/physDesc>\n                    \u003Chistory>\n                        \u003Corigin>\n                            \u003CorigPlace>\u003Cregion>Sicilia\u003C/region>\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"ancient\" ref=\"https://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462239\">Herbessus (?)\u003C/placeName>\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"modern\" ref=\"http://sws.geonames.org/11102431/\">Montagna di Marzo\u003C/placeName>\n                                \u003Cgeo>37.42658, 14.30061\u003C/geo>\n                            \u003C/origPlace>\n                            \u003CorigDate datingMethod=\"#julian\" evidence=\"archaeological-context material-context lettering\" notBefore-custom=\"-0500\" notAfter-custom=\"-0451\">500—450 BCE\u003C/origDate>\u003C!-- check date in Mussinano notes -->\n                        \u003C/origin>\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"found\">Found during the excavations (Soprintendenza alle Antichità di Siracusa, 1966—1968) in the area of the archaic necropolis, grave 109\u003Cgeo>37.42658, 14.30061\u003C!-- check and add more accurate coordinates here, these are the generic ones -->\u003C/geo>.\u003C/provenance>\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"observed\" subtype=\"autopsied\">None\u003C/provenance>\n                        \u003Cacquisition/>\n                    \u003C/history>\n                \u003C/msDesc>\n            \u003C/sourceDesc>\n        \u003C/fileDesc>\n        \u003CencodingDesc>\n            \u003Cp>Encoded following the latest EpiDoc guidelines\u003C/p>\n            \u003Cxi:include href=\"../alists/ISicily-taxonomies.xml\">\n                \u003Cxi:fallback>\n                    \u003Cp>Taxonomies for ISicily controlled values\u003C/p>\n                \u003C/xi:fallback>\n            \u003C/xi:include>\n            \u003Cxi:include href=\"../alists/charDecl.xml\">\n                \u003Cxi:fallback>\n                    \u003Cp>ISicily glyphs authority list\u003C/p>\n                \u003C/xi:fallback>\n            \u003C/xi:include>\n        \u003C/encodingDesc>\n        \u003CprofileDesc>\n            \u003CcalendarDesc>\n                \u003Ccalendar xml:id=\"julian\">\n                    \u003Cp>Julian Calendar\u003C/p>\n                \u003C/calendar>\n            \u003C/calendarDesc>\n            \u003ClangUsage>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"en\">English\u003C/language> \n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"it\">Italian\u003C/language> \n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"grc\">Ancient Greek\u003C/language> \n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"la\">Latin\u003C/language> \n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"he\">Hebrew\u003C/language> \n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"phn\">Phoenician\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"xpu\">Punic\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"osc\">Oscan\u003C/language> \n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"xly\">Elymian\u003C/language> \n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"scx\">Sikel\u003C/language>  \n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"sxc\">Sikan\u003C/language>  \n            \u003C/langUsage>\n            \u003CtextClass>\n                \u003Ckeywords scheme=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins.html\">\n                    \u003Cterm ana=\"#function.production-ownership\" ref=\"http://vocab.getty.edu/page/aat/300195926\">ownership (?)\u003C/term>\n                \u003C/keywords>\n            \u003C/textClass>\n        \u003C/profileDesc>\n        \u003CrevisionDesc status=\"draft\">\n            \u003ClistChange>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2020-10-05\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova normalised Unicode\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2020-10-08\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova updated list of languages\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2021-10-14\" who=\"#VM\">Valentina Mignosa added metadata, text\u003C/change>\n            \u003C/listChange>\n        \u003C/revisionDesc>\n    \u003C/teiHeader>\n    \u003Cfacsimile>\n        \u003Csurface type=\"front\">\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic020759_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic020759.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n         \u003C/surface>\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"primary\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"scx-Grek\" resp=\"#VM\">\u003C!--On the same object should be a second inscription (MMA 44.b) (?). -->\n                \u003Cab>    \n                   \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>\u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname>πυρρια\u003C/name>\u003C/persName>\n               \u003C/ab>          \n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" xml:space=\"preserve\" subtype=\"transliteration\" xml:lang=\"scx-Latn\">                 \n               \u003Cab>    \n                   \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>pyrria\n               \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\n                    \u003Capp>\n                        \u003Cnote>Text after Agostiniani, in Agostiniani, Albanese Procelli 2018.\u003C/note>\n                    \u003C/app>\n                \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\">\n                \u003Cp/>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"it\">\n                \u003Cp/>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#VM\">\n                \u003Cp>The masculine name Πυρρίας is common in Greek, also in Sicily. Πυρρι[ας] occurs for example in the environment of Gela, \n                    as shown by the graffito on black-glazed Attic skyphos (\u003Cref target=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic020500\">ISic020500\u003C/ref>; \u003Cref target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/65P7AM6N\">Arena IGASM II[2]\u003C/ref>, \n                    no. 54, pl. 19.3; \u003Cref target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/IFH7SBMP\">Manni Piraino 1980\u003C/ref>, p. 1804-1805, no. 42, pl. 11; \n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ\">SEG 29.0874\u003C/ref>) and by a defixio (\u003Cref target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/65P7AM6N\">Arena IGASM 2[2]\u003C/ref>, no. 45, l. 9), \n                    and it would therefore be no surprise to find it in the context of Montagna di Marzo.\n                    But we can also assume a masculine nominative case ending in -α, alien to Greek, but conceivable for other cases from Montagna di Marzo (Agostiniani 2018, p. 193), such as Ταμυρα (MMA 83; \n                    \u003Cref target=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic020752\">ISic020752\u003C/ref>) or \n                    Κακρυολα (MMA 81; \u003Cref target=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic020761\">ISic020761\u003C/ref>).\n                    Or, since the inscription is on a pyxis, a vessel generally associated with predominantly female use (Agostiniani 2018, 193, n.147), the name could be a feminine one, \n                    not otherwise attested in Greek.\u003C/p>\n                \n                \u003Cp>From a palaeographical point of view, it is interesting to note the use of 'normal' alpha (and not the arrow-shaped type), the rho type \n                    without the lower stroke (as occurs elsewhere and in the East tomb 31) and the upsilon type with a vertical bar, when most inscriptions use the V-type.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IAS2\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Agostiniani\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>Forthcoming\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>MMA 44a\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/UE7VX29V\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002519\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002519\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Agostiniani, Albanese Procelli\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>2018\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>193, fig. 119\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/RASC3AR5\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001345\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001345\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IGASM2[2]\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Arena\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>2002\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>54, pl. XIX.3\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/65P7AM6N\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001373\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001373\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"SEG\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>29.0874\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Manni Piraino\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1980\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>1804-1805, no.42, pl. 11\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/IFH7SBMP\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001765\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001765\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
